overview:
FreeLogoShop is a provider of FREE premium vector logos, business stationery and business cards. FreeLogoShop caters to entrepreneurs, startups, creatives and small businesses that are cash strapped and looking for affordable ways of creating a great brand identity. We have a huge catalog of templates to choose from that is growing daily.

FreeLogoShop can customize the logo, business stationery or business card to meet your particular needs, including changing the color, text, layout and even adding your company’s existing logo to the business stationery or business card. The fee to do so is very low and starts at $9. Please check out our website at http://www.freelogoshop.com.
